'''Michael Economides''' (Septembr 9, 1927 - October 24, 2021) was a Greek baker from Athens.

==Childhood and career==
Economides was born in an aircraft cock-pit mid-flight to Angie Economides (1894 - 1930). His father is unknown, though thought to be either the captain or co-pilot. Along with Angie, a camerawoman, Michael was also raised by his stepfather, school psychologist Stefans Mouskouri (1892 - 1982). Angie died in 1930 after being eaten by a shark on a beach trip.

